<riscos-prm>
<chapter title="Styled elements">

<section title="Interaction elements">

<p>Elements that are for interaction between the user and the system..</p>
<p>
<list>
    <item>User input: <userinput>I typed this</userinput></item>
    <item>System output: <systemoutput>The system responded with this</systemoutput></item>
    <item>Menu option: <menuoption>File</menuoption> <menuoption>Info</menuoption></item>
    <item>Action button: <actionbutton>Continue</actionbutton></item>
</list>
</p>
</section>

<section title="Environmental elements">
<p>Elements that describe parts of the system.</p>
<p>
<list>
    <item>Filename: <filename>ADFS::HardDisc4.$.Apps.!Paint</filename></item>
    <item>Filename (Windows): <filename type='windows'>C:\Program Files\</filename></item>
    <item>Filename (Unix): <filename type='unix'>/etc/hosts</filename></item>
    <item>Filename (URI): <filename type='uri'>http://example.com/</filename></item>
    <item>System Variable: <sysvar>CLI$Prompt</sysvar></item>
</list>
</p>
</section>

<section title="Internal elements">
<p>Elements that describe implementation of the system.</p>
<p>
<list>
    <item>Variable: <variable>errno</variable></item>
    <item>Command: <command>Help</command></item>
    <item>Function: <function>printf</function></item>
</list>
</p>
</section>

<section title="Presentational elements">
<p>Elements that are presentational only.</p>
<p>
<list>
    <item>Strong: <strong>I really mean this</strong></item>
    <item>Emphasis: <em>I also mean this</em></item>
    <item>Superscript: 2<sup>log2bpp</sup></item>
    <item>Subscript: idlen<sub>1</sub></item>
    <item>Line break: Text<br/>More text</item>
</list>
</p>
</section>

</chapter>

